Fixing the door with a steely glare, Cody backed up as far as the narrow passageway would allow. With a stifled shout,
he flung himself at the door, lowering his shoulder once again and driving it at the unyielding barrier. And indeed,
once again, it failed to yield. Cody stood, supported by the door, for a moment. Finally he let out a single, agonized
gasp, and sank to the floor, clutching at his battered shoulder.
